8.810005690235147e-17, \"text\": \"Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}, {\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999682306685, \"rank\": 3.0930739123560084e-08, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a three-time Olympic champion\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 375}, {\"ngram\": \"six medals\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 397}, {\"ngram\": \"three Games\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he has set his sights on a golden Games farewell in the French capital this summer on the pommel horse, his No1 apparatus.\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 508, \"end\": 514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8556446330214219, \"rank\": 0.1622716395378437, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his sights\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"a golden Games farewell\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 500}, {\"ngram\": \"the pommel horse\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The decision now feels right,\\\" Whitlock told BBC Breakfast.\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 608, \"end\": 616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.810005690235147e-17, \"text\": \"Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}, {\"begin\": 622, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Breakfast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BBC Breakfast\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Breakfast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Breakfast\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The decision\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Going for my final Olympic Games, it feels very, very strange talking about it, and it's almost hard to articulate what it's like.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my final Olympic Games\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a really nice mindset to be in, to think I will just give it all I have got.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really nice mindset\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ever since Rio where I was at my peak age, I think I have had questions thrown at me about when am I retiring.\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rio\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"my peak age\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 894}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have wanted to prove people wrong a lot of the way through my journey and I have always had the mindset of trying to do this for as long as I possibly can.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"my journey\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"the mindset\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now, I have given myself the opportunity for Willow [his daughter] to come and watch an Olympic Games because she could not in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253,